readable.content: A banner about a beauty parlor . A billboard advertising a vacation in on a run-down street . A dark haired man in white walks by a storefront under the sign for a beauty parlor . A man walks under a sign advertising a beauty parlor affixed to a dilapidated building . A man wearing white walks passed a shuttered building with an advertising banner over the door .
